# front public env example
# Source of truth: front/docs/frontend-spec.md

# Phantom Embedded app id from phantom.com/portal.
NEXT_PUBLIC_PHANTOM_APP_ID=your_phantom_app_id_here

# Do NOT put Solana RPC URLs or provider API keys in front env.
# RPC, Helius, Birdeye, Jupiter, risk-score and execution keys belong server-side
# in root/Vercel/backend configuration consumed by app/api/* or back/services/*.
